# Metzmatan's Mark v0.1.3

- Manifest URL (this specific version): <https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Mxblah/metzmatan/v0.1.3/system.json>
- System download URL: <https://github.com/Mxblah/metzmatan/releases/download/v0.1.3/metzmatan-v0.1.3.zip>

## Changes in version 0.1.3

### New Features

- Critical and Brutal Hits now properly apply the increased damage.

### Rule Changes

- Removed Critical Hit and Fumble tables, instead using simpler damage increase rules.
- Standardized and clarified many phrases.
- Added short Skill descriptions.
- Added several new monsters.
- Many, many smaller tweaks all across the rulebook.

### Technical

- Converted rulebook to asciidoc
- Added automatic rulebook pdf generation to release process
